{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a3f8a0046c","title":"李先念在财贸系统革命造反联络委员会“打倒姚依林大会”上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"da459f8c8a","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"a3f8a0046c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"姚依林","id":"1ce2886aee","type":"人物"},{"name":"工商交通和财政","id":"1ffce755c0","type":"主题"},{"name":"李先念","id":"33f01f9c5a","type":"人物"},{"name":"各级党政领导人","id":"a59dfa2519","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"637e61c517","name":"李先念"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c3b54e4605","type":"title","text":"李先念在财贸系统革命造反联络委员会“打倒姚依林大会”上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b363d5d2a7","type":"paragraph","text":"我坚决支持打倒姚依林大会的召开。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"95ac7980d0","type":"paragraph","text":"我也是犯了错误的，以前你们炮轰李先念火烧李先念，大方向是正确的，就是打倒李先念方向也是正确的，因为我犯了错误嘛！希望同志们对我还要继续批评。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da59e551f9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理接见你们时，你们提出要停姚依林的职。姚依林的问题，我已向总理反映过了，总理同意你们的要求（口号）。现在我代表中央、总理宣布停止姚依林在国务院财贸办公室副主任、中共中央财贸政治部主任的职务。（呼口号）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df2371975a","type":"paragraph","text":"我的错误，你们不要因为我而分两派，如果因为我分两派，我心里不安，感到惭愧。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"70c6dfbf92","type":"paragraph","text":"昨天总理接见你们，谈了抓革命促生产的问题，你们可以研究一下。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba29783a78","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒刘邓陶！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e219573f2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的革命路线胜利万岁！","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ce8fa89e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的领袖毛主席万岁！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a4ae691e2","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的毛泽东思想万岁！","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"a3f8a0046c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}